data.meta_description: 4th Grading Science - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document contains a science exam for 9th grade students on the topics of volcanoes, climate, and global warming. The exam includes 50 questions testing students on definitions, processes, and effects related to these topics. It provides context that the exam was given at Panique National High School in the Philippines for their 4th quarter of the 2018-2019 school year.
